===== dev =====

  * Port to OCaml 5.x compiler-libs API (replaces Printtyp.mark_loops,
    Types.get_desc, Odoc_html.text class merger, Module_apply_unit, ...).
  * Remove dead OCamlduce build rules and the obsolete commented-out
    OCSIGEN 1.2/1.3 wikidoc targets.
  * Populate the (previously empty) META file with description, dependencies
    (compiler-libs.common, ocamldoc, str) and archive/plugin entries so the
    package is usable via `ocamlfind`.
  * Modernise wikidoc.opam to opam 2.0 format. Add synopsis, description and
    license (GPL-2.0-or-later AND QPL-1.0); drop unused dependencies
    (`base-threads`, `base-unix`); require `ocaml >= 5.0`.
  * Add LICENSE / LICENSE.GPL-2 / LICENSE.QPL-1.0 documenting the
    per-component licensing (latex_of_wiki under GPL-2-or-later,
    odoc_wiki under QPL-1.0 as a derivative of the ocamldoc generators).
